A Russian taxi driver allegedly strangled his girlfriend to death before pushing her corpse around town in a wheelbarrow. 25-year-old Cabbie Filip Grigoryev, reportedly had an argument with his unnamed girlfriend before being caught on CCTV wheeling the barrow around roads. Filip who drove his girlfriend’s body around town for an hour eventually dumped his girlfriend’s corpse in the corridor of the 11th floor of a block of flats on Gollandskaya Street before fleeing. Police have arrested Filip after watching the CCTV footage.